        <Parent_String>oil burners [300179668], burners by fuel type [300179658], burners (oil lamp components) [300179654], lighting device components [300037653], furnishings components [300241953], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
